      "text": "the Bureau to be used in their monthly publication, \"[REDACTED]\" [REDACTED] was identified",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "as [REDACTED] as well as [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "[REDACTED] In 1957 a brief inquiry concerning the Baltimore",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
