      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "ment of 121 students. It was indicated to be affiliated with the [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "[REDACTED] and its principal officers were ministers of the Church of God. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "reportedly holds a [REDACTED] degree and is a graduate of LaSalle Law",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "University. Stranges has been given permission to reprint two of my previously",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
